{"type":"ScenarioReference","class":"Mythos","tokens":{"front":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, choose a barricade token in play and remove it from the game."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"Reveal another token. If you fail, resolve the hunter or patrol keyword on an enemy in play."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, place 1 of your clues on your location."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. If you fail, place a doom on a bystander asset of your choice."}},"back":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. Remove the barricade token closest to you from the game."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"Reveal another token. If you fail, resolve the hunter or patrol keyword on each enemy in play."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. If you fail, place 1 of your clues on your location for each point you failed by."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. Place a doom on a bystander asset of your choice"}}},"TtsZoopGuid":"e72cb2c6-a4d4-4802-bf41-0ff42dcee899"}
